-as-sebi-approves-launch-of-fo-contracts-for-bse-sensex-next-30-index-9943078.html","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-03-05T09:44:25","source":"News 18"},{"id":"516787","title":"BSE secures SEBI approval to introduce derivatives for Sensex Next 30 Index.\nThis move aims to broaden BSE's product offerings in derivatives trading.","summary":"BSE secures SEBI approval to introduce derivatives for Sensex Next 30 Index.\nThis move aims to broaden BSE's product offerings in derivatives trading.","url":"","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-03-04T16:50:15","source":"Livesquawk"},{"id":"512491","title":"NSE CEO Chauhan proposes F&O qualifying criteria to curb speculation, protect small investors, citing regulatory concerns.\nBSE shares drop 3% to ₹2,716; Angel One falls 4.5% to ₹235.5 after trading adjusted for a 1:10 stock split.","summary":"NSE CEO Chauhan proposes F&O qualifying criteria to curb speculation, protect small investors, citing regulatory concerns.\nBSE shares drop 3% to ₹2,716; Angel One falls 4.5% to ₹235.5 after trading adjusted for a 1:10 stock split.","url":"https://www.cnbctv18.com/market/nse-md-ceo-ashishkumar-chauhan-minimum-qualifying-criteria-fno-rising-retail-losses-bse-angel-one-share-19859456.htm","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-27T14:20:29","source":"CNBC TV 18"},{"id":"505302","title":"BSE faces declining share in a shrinking derivatives market.\nEquity derivatives trading fell in Feb 2026, even before higher STT rates.","summary":"BSE faces declining share in a shrinking derivatives market.\nEquity derivatives trading fell in Feb 2026, even before higher STT rates.","url":"https://www.cnbctv18.com/market/stocks/bse-is-losing-share-in-a-shrinking-market-for-derivatives-ws-l-19854457.htm","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-20T12:11:18","source":"CNBC TV 18"},{"id":"505209","title":"BSE's February ADTO dropped 21%, while NSE saw a 7% decline MoM.\nThe data highlights a notable reduction in trading activity for both exchanges.","summary":"BSE's Febru